sign rules combat~
&z 
&W ===========================================================================
&R                  " T H E   R U L E S   O F   C O M B A T "                 
&z 
&z  To attack a monster, type: &WKILL monster
&z  To flee from combat, type: &WFLEE
&z 
&z  You will gain experience for hitting a monster, using some of your combat 
&z  skills or spells, and for defeating a monster.
&z 
&z  Fleeing will cause you to loose experience, and may not always work. Note 
&z  that some monsters will pursue you if you flee...
&z 
&R  CAUTION: &WSome monsters will attack without provocation!
&z 
&R                       THOSE, ARE THE RULES OF COMBAT.                      
&W ===========================================================================
~
